Our last and best predictor, that we call SNPMuSIC, combines the deleteriousness index I of the ANN model (Eq. (8)) with the Provean score, thus defining the \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
